lead_paragraph: Gunmen involved in a rare terrorist attack in Jordan had a large supply of weapons, explosives and suicide vests, an official said.

byline.contributor: Dan Levin contributed reporting from New York.

headline.print_headline: In Jordan, Weapons Discovery Suggests Slain Gunmen Planned Multiple Attacks
headline.main: Cache of Weapons Suggests Gunmen in Jordan Were Planning Multiple Attacks
